        com.instantiations.assist.eclipse.audit.modifierOrder.comment=Nope. Too nit-picky. It's way more important that you just get the modifiers exactly right; no more and no less than the exact one's needed. (Aside\: So what if it's a Sun standard, the Java language doesn't require it and the Sun standards are the weakest I've ever read among the well knon Java standards). --Rusty
