        com.instantiations.assist.eclipse.audit.disallowDefaultPackage.comment=There are good reasons to place a few classes in the default namespace. If this rule had a parameter pane for defining exceptions, we would possibly turn it on, but it does not, and it is not a big or typical enough voilation to ask Instantaions to add such a panel, so we will not ask them. We will just not use it. --Rusty 07/29/06
