        com.instantiations.assist.eclipse.hibernate.declareAccessors.severity=0
        com.instantiations.assist.eclipse.audit.spaceAfterCommas.comment=Yeah, set your code free of the cramps\! Let it be quickly and easily readable by someone over 40 yrs old (and even younger people with eyes not as good as yours). Yes, this actually happens in the world--not everyone can see as well as you.\r\n\r\nTypically only people under 40 could possibly convience themselves that this\r\n\r\nfoo(x,y,a,b,c,dog,cat);\r\n\r\nis as easily read and causes no more eye strain than\r\n\r\nfoo( x, y, a, b, c, dog, cat );\r\n\r\n--Rusty
