        com.instantiations.assist.eclipse.audit.missingUpdateInFor.comment=Many people believe quite the contray--they think you should almost always use for loops instead of while loops to reduce loop counter/loop iterater variable scope.  Another rule in this audit tool actually even allows you to require the for loop. Use the loop structure you think best for each context. --Rusty
