        com.instantiations.assist.eclipse.audit.numericLiterals.comment=Yep. If you need them, decalare them as static finals and do this\r\n\r\nx \= MY_STATIC_FINAL;\r\n\r\nrather than\r\n\r\nx \= 42;\r\n\r\n--Rusty\r\n\r\nAgain, the above is all dreamy and pretty, but this rule is flagging as violations the setting of intial StringBuilder and HashMap sizing. That's too restrictive. --Rusty (8/29/05).
