            <setting id="com.perforce.team.ui.preferences.CHANGELIST_DESCRIPTIONS" value="Added test.  Fixed exposed bug.###The read from DS3 target id must be set on chunks to be serviced by a
DS3 target.###Fixed bug found in manual testing where chunk number collisions can occur
since we don&apos;t ensure incrementing chunk numbers on the source of a GET job
that is farming out part of the GET to a DS3 target.###Fixed bugs and added tests based on manual testing.

We failed to parse the get job created in the Ds3ConnectionImpl due
to attempting to unmarshal into the wrong type.###Fixed bug where API was misleading for getting readable tapes from
PersistenceTargetUtil.###Logging improvement:

Log at a WARN level when exhaustion occurs, and at an INFO level when
we check to see if we&apos;re exhausted and we are.###Re-generated self docs.###Now injecting the job id all the way down the stack when creating GET jobs
in a replicated manner.###Added tests.  Fixed exposed bugs.###wip injecting ds3 connection factory into JobCreatorImpl###"/>
            <setting id="com.perforce.team.ui.shelvedcolumns" value="Changelist=100###Date=100###User=100###Workspace=100###Description=100###"/>
            <setting id="com.perforce.team.ui.submitted.FILE_FOLDER_HISTORY" value="${eclipse.drive}\perforce\rubygem-spectra_cli\...###"/>
            <setting id="com.perforce.team.ui.submittedcolumns" value="Changelist=100###Date=100###User=100###Workspace=100###Description=100###"/>
            <setting id="pref_resolve_migrated_to_2012.3" value="true"/>
        </pref_store>
    </plugin>
